import React from 'react';
import KeypadRow from './KeypadRow/KeypadRow';
import Button from '../../../components/Button/Button';
const keypad = () => (
  <section className="keypad">
    <KeypadRow>
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
    </KeypadRow>
    
    <KeypadRow>
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
    </KeypadRow>
    
    <KeypadRow>
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
    </KeypadRow>
    
    <KeypadRow>
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
    </KeypadRow>
    
    <KeypadRow>
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
    </KeypadRow>

    <KeypadRow>
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
    </KeypadRow>
  </section>
);
export default keypad;
